ED_Title: Comprehensive review of the whole question of peacekeeping operations in all their aspects
ED_DecisionText: At its 45th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2023, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee).19 (Footnote: A/78/422.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
